Task
Get an array of letters
An array containing names is given. Get an array of the first letters of the names contained in the original array.
Write a function arrayOfFirstLetters that takes an array of strings names as an argument and returns an array containing the first letters of the strings in the original array.
Example:
• the arrayOfFirstLetters (["Alice", "Bob"]) function must return ["A", "B"];
• the arrayOfFirstLetters (["Kate"]) function must return ["K"];
• the arrayOfFirstLetters ([]) function must return [].

Solution
function arrayOfFirstLetters (names) {
  let newArr = [];
  for (let i = 0; i <names.length; i ++) {
   newArr.push (names [i] [0]);
}
return newArr;
}
